                            <note rend="inline" type="source">711.90f2/27: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Ambassador in Great Britain (<persName type="to">Mellon</persName>)</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-11-18T17:00:00-05:00">November 18, 1932—5 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>285. Draft note enclosed with your despatch 472, November 3 is
                                approved.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
